=== 爆紅 ===
儘管《恐鬼症》在2020年9月中旬左右首次發佈，但其直到10月初有許多[[Twitch|Twitch]]實況主和YouTuber，例如[[PewDiePie|PewDiePie]]、[[xQc|xQc]]、[[Pokimane|Pokimane]]、[[Jacksepticeye|Jacksepticeye]]、[[Sodapoppin|Sodapoppin]]和[[Markiplier|Markiplier]]等都在玩這遊戲後才開始為人熟知<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.essentiallysports.com/pewdiepie-returns-to-horror-games-with-phasmophobia-esports-news/|title=PewDiePie Returns to Horror Games with Phasmophobia|last=Biswas|first=Souhardya|date=2020-10-09|website=Essentially Sports|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115193418/https://www.essentiallysports.com/pewdiepie-returns-to-horror-games-with-phasmophobia-esports-news/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/au/what-deserves-to-be-the-next-streaming-phenomenon-like-among-us-or-phasmophobia/|title=What deserves to be the next streaming phenomenon like Among Us or Phasmophobia?|date=2020-10-23|website=PC Gamer|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029215735/https://www.pcgamer.com/au/what-deserves-to-be-the-next-streaming-phenomenon-like-among-us-or-phasmophobia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這可能是因為遊戲在萬聖節開始前後提供搶先體驗，且其特點類似於《[[P.T.|P.T.]]》的緣故<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/10/twitchs-latest-horror-sensation-phasmophobia-has-streamers-screaming-at-each-other/|title=Twitch’s Latest Horror Sensation, Phasmophobia, Has Streamers Screaming (At Each Other)|last=Grayson|first=Nathan|date=2020-10-15|website=Kotaku|accessdate=2020-10-17|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213013658/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2020/10/twitchs-latest-horror-sensation-phasmophobia-has-streamers-screaming-at-each-other/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也有可能是因著第二波[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]的開始，導致許多人須呆在家裡而導致人氣急升<ref name="CBR">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbr.com/phasmophobia-indie-horror-game-ghosts/|title=Phasmophobia Is the BEST Indie Horror Game to Play This Halloween|last=Creswell|first=Jacob|date=2020-10-20|website=CBR|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070000/https://www.cbr.com/phasmophobia-indie-horror-game-ghosts/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著大批玩家因受歡迎的實況主遊玩而蜂擁而至，黑客們也在《恐鬼症》發行後的第二週肆虐，他們主要通過[[突發驚嚇|突發驚嚇]]和生成大量物品的方式來影響玩家<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.essentiallysports.com/phasmophobia-is-scarier-than-ever-but-not-because-of-the-horror-esports-news/|title=Phasmophobia Is Scarier than Ever But Not Because of the Horror|last=Sharma|first=Aakrit|date=2020-10-20|website=Essentially Sports|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023033411/https://www.essentiallysports.com/phasmophobia-is-scarier-than-ever-but-not-because-of-the-horror-esports-news/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中一個最令人關注是「狙擊實況主」的問題，某些黑客甚至在事前更改其人物模組成為[[NSFW|NSFW]]的內容後加入實況主所開的房間，試圖令後者收到實況網站的警告或因發放不當內容而被封台<ref name="Jumpscare">{{Cite web|url=https://www.denofgeek.com/games/phasmophobia-hackers-jump-scare-streamer-reactions/|title=Phasmophobia Hackers Are Using Jump Scares to Haunt Streamers|last=Byrd|first=Matthew|date=2020-10-20|website=Den of Geek|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117020800/https://www.denofgeek.com/games/phasmophobia-hackers-jump-scare-streamer-reactions/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/phasmophobia-hackers-are-terrorizing-streamers-with-jump-scares/1100-6483510/|title=Phasmophobia Hackers Are Terrorizing Streamers With Jump Scares|last=Williams|first=Hayley|date=2020-10-19|website=GameSpot|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204150532/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/phasmophobia-hackers-are-terrorizing-streamers-with-jump-scares/1100-6483510/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Kinetic Games隨後發放多次更新，期望解決問題，也建議實況主在遊玩前表明已有四個或以上的玩家準備遊玩，或直接運行Beta版的遊戲以避開黑客<ref name="Jumpscare"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/phasmophobia-devs-working-on-fix-for-hackers-spawning-in-even-more-jump-scares|title=Phasmophobia Devs Working on Fix for Hackers Spawning in Even More Jump Scares|last=Oloman|first=Jordan|date=2020-10-20|website=IGN|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118052708/https://www.ign.com/articles/phasmophobia-devs-working-on-fix-for-hackers-spawning-in-even-more-jump-scares|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在Twitch上，《恐鬼症》的觀看數呈指數式增長，並曾在10月中旬超越《[[我們之中|我們之中]]》、《[[堡垒之夜：空降行动|堡垒之夜：空降行动]]》、《[[FIFA_21|FIFA 21]]》和《[[原神|原神]]》等遊戲，成為前5名觀看數最多的遊戲之一<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/phasmophobia-steam-twitch-top-10|title=Phasmophobia Is a New Steam and Twitch Sensation|last=Joe|first=Skrebels|date=2020-10-09|website=IGN|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118170821/https://www.ign.com/articles/phasmophobia-steam-twitch-top-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/phasmophobia-is-blowing-up-on-steam-and-twitch/1100-6483324/|title=Phasmophobia Is Blowing Up On Steam And Twitch|last=Garst|first=Aron|date=2020-10-14|website=GameSpot|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101075315/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/phasmophobia-is-blowing-up-on-steam-and-twitch/1100-6483324/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據在線玩家跟蹤器GitHyp的數據，該作在10月31日左右達到約11萬名活躍玩家的峰值<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.githyp.com/phasmophobia-186147/?tab=player-count|title=Phasmophobia Player Count|website=GitHyp|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119094844/https://www.githyp.com/phasmophobia-186147/?tab=player-count|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/phasmophobia/top-five-most-played-steam|title=Phasmophobia hit Steam’s top five most-played games this weekend|last=Sledge|first=Ben|date=2020-10-12|website=PCGamesN|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120193226/https://www.pcgamesn.com/phasmophobia/top-five-most-played-steam|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《恐鬼症》亦在2020年10月後兩週成為Steam的最暢銷遊戲<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/phasmophobia/sales|title=Phasmophobia is out-selling Baldur’s Gate 3, Cyberpunk 2077, and The Outer Worlds on Steam|last=McGlynn|first=Anthony|date=2020-10-26|website=PCGamesN|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230122741/https://www.pcgamesn.com/phasmophobia/sales|dead-url=no}}</ref>，期間甚至比《[[糖豆人：终极淘汰赛|糖豆人：终极淘汰赛]]》和《[[赛博朋克2077|赛博朋克2077]]》{{link-en|預訂|Pre-order|預訂版}}還要多<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/au/indie-ghost-hunter-phasmophobia-is-a-steam-top-seller/|title=Indie ghost hunter Phasmophobia is a Steam top seller|last=Brown|first=Fraser|date=2020-10-12|website=PC Gamer|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018130043/https://www.pcgamer.com/au/indie-ghost-hunter-phasmophobia-is-a-steam-top-seller/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.essentiallysports.com/phasmophobia-jumps-a-spot-on-steam-chart-to-reach-an-all-time-high-pewdiepie-esports-among-us-news/|title=Phasmophobia Jumps a Spot on Steam Charts to Reach an All-Time High|last=Shwetang|first=Parthsarthy|date=2020-10-19|website=Essentially Sports|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112033956/https://www.essentiallysports.com/phasmophobia-jumps-a-spot-on-steam-chart-to-reach-an-all-time-high-pewdiepie-esports-among-us-news/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

